    Andalusia, the most southern province of Spain and the European tourist Mecca, was chosen as the perfect location for the Spanish Village international business accelerator. This region is famous for its splendid climate: 300 sunny days per year and the average annual air temperature of +18°C. The coast of Andalusia washed by the Atlantic Ocean and the Mediterranean Sea is perfect for bathing and also kite and wind surfing. Andalusia is widely known for its spectacular sea and mountain landscapes.
